  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Falls and injurious falls are common among elderly people. The aim of the study is to test a
      model of multifactorial fall intervention in a Danish population of elderly sustaining a
      fall. Focus is on prevention of further falls, patients views on fall prevention and a
      cost-effectiveness analysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
