  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  65 years old or older

          -  Having been treated in emergency department or submitted to hospital after a fall

          -  Living in the Glostrup area.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Fall due to strong external force, new apoplexia cerebri, epileptic seizure, alcohol
             intoxication.

          -  Known cognitive impairment

          -  Not able to walk prior to fall

          -  Living in institution

          -  Planned geriatric intervention.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
